LINUX DOWNLOAD

1. Extract the archive
`tar -xzvf black-session-0.0.0.tar.gz`

2. Navigate to the folder
`cd black-session-0.0.0`

3. Grant execute permissions
`chmod +x black-session`

4. Run 
`./black-session`


(Optional) Install as an app:
`sudo mv ~/black-session-0.0.0 /opt/black-session`
`sudo ln -s /opt/black-session/black-session /usr/local/bin/black-session`

`black-session`
